Paper: hep-th/9603148

Date: 1996-03-22

Title: Coupling supergravity to non-supersymmetric matter

Comments: 11 pages, LATEX, references added

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B390 (1997) 172-178

By introducing a nonlinearly transforming goldstino fieldnon-super\-sym\-metric matter can be coupled to supergravity. This implies thepossibility of coupling a standard model with one Higgs to supergravity.